ttps://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/5/b/5b360632-9c81-4b9c-8b9f-ac0b51c974a0.jpg?1782689916", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/5/b/5b360632-9c81-4b9c-8b9f-ac0b51c974a0.jpg?1782689916", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/dsc/74/portent?utm_source=api", "local": "img/portent/e744dbb6-2d56-462a-8d49-d79c73944048.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Charcoal Diamond", "set": "CLB", "html": "Every facet a <mark>portent</mark> of Kelemvor&#x27;s inevitable judgment.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/f/0/f0475c79-bc7f-4de8-a020-226bc658d303.jpg?1782701158"}, {"card": "Femeref Scouts", "set": "MIR", "html": "&quot;The days before the war were filled with strange <mark>portents</mark>: scouts and herders spoke of villages reduced to ash, of farmers taken from their fields, and of foul beasts roaming the plains in packs. I know, for I spoke to them all.&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/0/60192ded-689b-4cc5-9293-bff52924089b.jpg?1782721466"}, {"card": "Soothsayer Adept", "set": "STX", "html": "One of the first lessons divination students learn is how to recognize the difference between a <mark>portent</mark> and a simple surface ripple.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/e/b/eb93c9d2-88eb-403d-bb67-8e8b0462ac27.jpg?1782704980"}, {"card": "Divinity of Pride", "set": "C13", "html": "&quot;She spoke of mystery and <mark>portent</mark>, of such unfathomable things that my mind screamed for pity.&quot;\n—*The Seer&#x27;s Parables*", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/e/2e40c246-276b-45f1-ac86-f15c0df62a08.jpg?1782713610"}, {"card": "Witch's Familiar", "set": "M15", "html": "Some bog witches practice the strange art of batrachomancy, reading <mark>portents</mark> in the number, size, and color of warts on a toad&#x27;s hide.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/8/c/8c9f3b3b-de16-4ae5-844e-1373e0f84469.jpg?1782713210"}, {"card": "Birds of Paradise", "set": "MSC", "html": "The migration of the cranes is believed to be a <mark>portent</mark> of coming abundance in Wakanda.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/4/9/492c2f9a-51e7-4e0f-9899-23bf43ea988b.jpg?1782682523"}, {"card": "Prismatic Omen", "set": "SHM", "html": "In times of <mark>portent</mark>, the land sculpts itself in accordance with the sigils burned on the sky.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/e/7/e75594cc-de47-49f2-9a8b-ba76c576368e.jpg?1782716143"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Porcine Portent // Lend a Ham", "set": "YWOE", "html": "When Porcine <mark>Portent</mark> enters, conjure a card of your choice from the Three Pigs spellbook onto the battlefield.\nBoars you control get +1/+1.\nExile target creature. You gain 1 life for each Boar you control."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/8/5/8599e2dd-9164-4da3-814f-adccef3b9497.jpg?1782690584", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/8/5/8599e2dd-9164-4da3-814f-adccef3b9497.jpg?1782690584", "card": "Portent of Calamity"}}